Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw laughed, but inside she was saying...oh, slag! If she did 
transform, then her cover--her plan would be blown to the Pit. But she had 
to keep calm.

"Transform? Transform to prove this clone wrong?" Slag it, she was winging 
it. "I am quite confortable in this form." She sneered. "Look at him. Just 
look at him! He is not the Dinobot that betrayed Megatron. This creature 
that stands in your midst is apparently a mere clone, perhaps a drone. Look 
him, and look at me. I am the Dinobot that had followed Primal for the glory 
of victory for the Maximals. I have not returned to argue the fact that I am 
true. Look at me!" She brought her two forepaws to her narrow chest.
